data.description: Great family home in the heart of Purcell. Current owner is using the 3rd bedroom as a 2nd living. Beautiful real hardwood floors in great condition. The large living flows to a well lit dining. The kitchen has a separate dining area. Fridge is negotiable. The secondary bedrooms share a full bath. Lots of Upgrade in the past few years. New Hot water heater. This home sits on a corner lot!
